<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,382,583,610]" italics="true" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">Neurotoma saltuum</emphasis>
(Linnaeus,1758)
</taxonomicName>
</heading>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="36" pageNumber="37" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="36.[151,1437,583,718]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">
<bibRefCitation author="Sundukov, Yu. N." box="[151,346,619,645]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37" pagination="20 - 117" refId="ref79858" refString="Sundukov, Yu. N. (2017) Suborder Symphyta - Sawflies and wood wasps. In: Lelej, A. S., Proshchalykin, M. Yu. &amp; Loktionov, V. M. (Eds.), Annotated catalogue of the Hymenoptera of Russia. Vol. I. Symphyta and Apocrita: Aculeata. Proceedings of the Zoological Institute of the Russian Academy of Sciences, Supplement 6, pp. 20 - 117." type="journal article" year="2017">Sundukov (2017)</bibRefCitation>
included the Korean Peninsula in the distribution of this species. As fully discussed by 
<bibRefCitation author="Shinohara, A." pageId="36" pageNumber="37" pagination="87 - 117" refId="ref75956" refString="Shinohara, A. (1980) East Asian species of the genus Neurotoma (Hymenoptera: Pamphiliidae). Transactions of the Shikoku Entomological Society, 15, 87 - 117." type="journal article" year="1980">Shinohara (1980)</bibRefCitation>
, this record is wrong. 
<bibRefCitation author="Shinohara, A. &amp; Choi, J. - K. &amp; Lee, J. - W." box="[472,739,655,681]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37" pagination="593 - 599" refId="ref77365" refString="Shinohara, A., Choi, J. - K. &amp; Lee, J. - W. (2018 a) The webspinning sawfly genus Neurotoma (Hymenoptera, Pamphiliidae) of South Korea: Neurotoma silla sp. nov. and a key to species. Zootaxa, 4444 (5), 593 - 599. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4444.5.7" type="journal article" year="2018">
Shinohara 
<emphasis box="[591,646,655,681]" italics="true" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">et al.</emphasis>
(2018a)
</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="Lee, J. - W. &amp; Choi, J. - K. &amp; Park, B." box="[791,975,655,682]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37" pagination="1 - 96" refId="ref74711" refString="Lee, J. - W., Choi, J. - K. &amp; Park, B. (2019) Synoptic list of Symphyta (Hymenoptera) in Korea. Journal of Species Research, 8, 1 - 96." type="journal article" year="2019">
Lee 
<emphasis box="[839,895,655,681]" italics="true" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">et al.</emphasis>
(2019)
</bibRefCitation>
did not include this species in the Korean fauna. There is no evidence for the occurrence of this species in 
<collectingCountry box="[871,943,692,718]" name="South Korea" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">Korea</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
